    "Emerging methods like Spiking SNNs and SOMs introduce energy efficiency and intuitive visualizations, while XAI fosters trust by offering transparency in model decisions.",
    "Together, these methodologies address the increasing demands of modern telecom networks, ensuring proactive, scalable, and interpretable solutions for anomaly detection.",
